  Browser --> Nginx
  Nginx --> API
  Nginx -.-> WS
  Browser -. direct .-> API
  Browser <-->|live updates| WS
  WS --> SVC
  SEC -. inbound filter chain .-> API
  API --> SVC
  SVC --> DB
  SVC --> FS
